# CODEOWNERS — routes review requests to maintainers.
#
# DeltaSharp is early-stage; @khaines is the founding maintainer and default owner,
# so every path resolves to a real owner today. The trailing "# persona:<slug>"
# note on each source rule records the specialist that will own the area as
# maintainers join — swap @khaines for that real handle or team then. The persona
# roster and the label taxonomy live in docs/persona/agents/README.md and
# docs/planning/label-taxonomy.md.
#
# NOTE ON REVIEW ENFORCEMENT: branch protection on `main` does not currently
# require code-owner review (single-maintainer phase). That is a documented
# exception; see docs/planning/label-taxonomy.md ("Branch protection and required
# review"). CODEOWNERS still auto-requests review from the owner below.

# Default owner for everything
*                               @khaines

